research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Alvarado, TX, include the Mayor, Mayor Pro-Tem, and five Council Members. Information was primarily sourced from the City of Alvarado's official government pages. There was a discrepancy in one source regarding the Mayor Pro-Tem, with the Texas State Directory Online listing Lydia Moon, while the Alvarado city website consistently lists Kevin Thomas. The information from the Alvarado city website was prioritized for accuracy. Specific ward/place designations were included where explicitly found.
